m_q.target_metric: List of leagues (excluding NPSL) that the NY men's soccer team has played in
sub_questions: What distinct leagues appear in the data?
Which of those leagues are not NPSL?
Are there any leagues with incomplete or placeholder entries that should be excluded?

scale_issues: Year column contains mixed formats: single years (2008) and year ranges (2010-11, 2016-17)
Some Regular Season values contain both ranking and conference information

format_notes: Year column contains special characters (en dash) in year ranges
Regular Season column contains comma-separated ranking and conference data

constraints: Each row represents one season/team performance
League column should contain valid league names
Division values should be integers 4 or 5 based on sample
derived_filters: Exclude rows with placeholder league names if any
statistical_tests: Verify no null values in League column for filtered rows
output_format_requirements: Each league should appear only once
